🚀 THE ASTRONAUT – Official Trailer (2025) | Laurence Fishburne Sci-Fi Thriller 🚀
Space holds no mercy. The Astronaut is the pulse-pounding new sci-fi thriller where isolation, secrets, and cosmic danger collide.

When veteran astronaut Dr. Owen Grant (Laurence Fishburne) returns from a classified deep-space mission, he finds the world changed — and something came back with him. Haunted by visions, memories that don't match, and strange signals from beyond, he must race to uncover what happened… before it kills him.
